## How to Run

1. Clone the repository:
   git clone https://github.com/sharroufdani/sms-classifier.git

2. Install dependencies:
   pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Train the model (optional if clf.joblib exists):
   python classifier.py

4. Run the Streamlit app:
   streamlit run app.py

5. Access public URL:
   If using ngrok, replace the placeholder token with your personal token to expose the app publicly.
